{"tid":2190933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團體調查指8成基層學生無適合電腦裝置學習","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:56:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb9b676d6b517b36c372cb1ba2c1de5ed529d6c","tid":2190933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"關注學童發展權利聯席就基層家庭網上學習支援情況，進行調查，發現有8成學生無適合的電腦裝置，例如手提電腦及平板電腦。亦有近7成受訪家長表示，學校無參與關愛基金下有關資助清貧學生購買電腦的援助項目。<br />\n<br />\n調查在7月透過網上進行，上月底至本月初再以網上問卷形式訪問這批家長，收回900份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n有就讀中四的學生表示，早於3月向學校填寫申請表借用電腦，但到8月都未有回覆，網上交功課要同學代交。亦有家長表示，家中3個小朋友要用一部二手電腦，年紀最小的兒子要讓哥哥上課。<br />\n<br />\n聯席建議，將關愛基金電腦津貼計劃擴闊至所有清貧中小學生，將申請手續改為由基層家長自行申請，以及擴闊「為低收入劏房住戶改善家居援助計劃」的受惠項目，協助基層家庭購買電腦設備。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548125-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548125-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=3678c4bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548125-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6afbe49b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548125-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"acf30e3493c3737d774ae7d364992477c7d86e2b","tid":2190933,"uid":46587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"我建議擴闊「為低收入劏房住戶改善家居援助計劃」的受惠項目，協助基層家庭購買condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b95b4572c2359fcc6785ef20d7cc31da56196b","tid":2190933,"uid":294121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"好多基層都無樓住<br />\n可否一人一個500呎單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88535bd951b76f0ddeddb07369fdd4690ee220a","tid":2190933,"uid":295602,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"基層電腦問題, 一律叫佢搵明愛"},{"pid":"13996b330837e5b9897537e2104fd7db11ef3a92","tid":2190933,"uid":330457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acf30e3493c3737d774ae7d364992477c7d86e2b","tid":2190933,"uid":46587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"我建議擴闊「為低收入劏房住戶改善家居援助計劃」的受惠項目，協助基層家庭購買condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"呢個實際過資助個家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b887876e07e692f174fb1257697a463756e3c1","tid":2190933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf30e3493c3737d774ae7d364992477c7d86e2b","tid":2190933,"uid":46587,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"我建議擴闊「為低收入劏房住戶改善家居援助計劃」的受惠項目，協助基層家庭購買condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9f410cb27afe53796744a88b28d88a7cccfb53","tid":2190933,"uid":129030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e88535bd951b76f0ddeddb07369fdd4690ee220a","tid":2190933,"uid":295602,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"基層電腦問題, 一律叫佢搵明愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"$200 甚至免費有一部電腦<br />\n仲有任何團體話無電腦都係居心叵測"},{"pid":"0c79120b81d696d4a0ade55a5c873bf743637160","tid":2190933,"uid":224533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"適合的電腦=MacBook Pro 16吋"},{"pid":"6a70f2de9e7a4af84d43fa8630c3cd26e07fe71c","tid":2190933,"uid":62226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"「調查在7月透過網上進行」<br />\n<br />\n下？"},{"pid":"d57b5621f5e008ce3a23b98490326ce42f8ff0e2","tid":2190933,"uid":7468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTi